<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFHoldrenCarl_Kaysen2003">Holdren, John P.; Carl Kaysen (2003). <a href="http://www.amacad.org/publications/bulletin/fall2003/holdren.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.amacad.org/publications/bulletin/fall2003/holdren.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Environmental Change and the Human Condition"</a> (PDF). <i>Bulletin Fall</i>. 24-31<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.amacad.org/publications/bulletin/fall2003/holdren.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.amacad.org/publications/bulletin/fall2003/holdren.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.amacad.org/publications/bulletin/fall2003/holdren.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-08-10</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Environmental+Change+and+the+Human+Condition&amp;rft.atitle=Bulletin+Fall&amp;rft.aulast=Holdren&amp;rft.aufirst=John+P.&amp;rft.au=Holdren%2C+John+P.&amp;rft.au=Carl+Kaysen&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pages=24-31&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amacad.org%2Fpublications%2Fbulletin%2Ffall2003%2Fholdren.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kardashev_scale"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFDordrecht1985">Dordrecht, D. (1985). "Exponential Expansion: Galactic Destiny or Technological Hubris?". in B. R. Finney, M. D. Papagiannis. <i>The Search for Extraterrestrial Life: Recent Developments</i>. Reidel Publ. Co.. pp.&#160;465–463.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Exponential+Expansion%3A+Galactic+Destiny+or+Technological+Hubris%3F&amp;rft.atitle=The+Search+for+Extraterrestrial+Life%3A+Recent+Developments&amp;rft.aulast=Dordrecht&amp;rft.aufirst=D.&amp;rft.au=Dordrecht%2C+D.&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B465%E2%80%93463&amp;rft.pub=Reidel+Publ.+Co.&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kardashev_scale"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><a href="http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/S/Shkadov.html" class="external text" title="http://www.daviddarling.info/encyclopedia/S/Shkadov.html" rel="nofollow">Shkadov Thruster</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Korotayev" title="Korotayev" class="mw-redirect">Korotayev</a> A., Malkov A., Khaltourina D. <i>Introduction to Social Macrodynamics: Compact Macromodels of the World System Growth.</i> Moscow: URSS, 2006. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/5484004144" class="internal">ISBN 5-484-00414-4</a> <a href="http://urss.ru/cgi-bin/db.pl?cp=&amp;lang=en&amp;blang=en&amp;list=14&amp;page=Book&amp;id=34250" class="external autonumber" title="http://urss.ru/cgi-bin/db.pl?cp=&amp;lang=en&amp;blang=en&amp;list=14&amp;page=Book&amp;id=34250" rel="nofollow">[1]</a>.</li>
</ul>
