<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFKardashev1997">Kardashev, Nikolai (March 1997). "Cosmology and Civilizations". <i>Astrophysics and Space Science</i> <b>252</b>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Cosmology+and+Civilizations&amp;rft.jtitle=Astrophysics+and+Space+Science&amp;rft.aulast=Kardashev&amp;rft.aufirst=Nikolai&amp;rft.au=Kardashev%2C+Nikolai&amp;rft.date=March+1997&amp;rft.volume=252&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Kardashev_scale"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
